Rimwe rematambudziko makuru rine mudzidzi nekunyora rondedzero kutora zvese kubva munzira uye kupedzisa rondedzero nenguva. Vanhu vazhinji vane chinyorwa c

Vazhinji vatengesi vanoshandisa chidimbu chimwe chetekinoroji chavanofarira kana kugadzikana nacho uye vanofuratira vamwe. Ini ndiri mutsigiri mukuru wekushandisa otomatiki uye mushambadzi achishandisa mameseji avo munzira ipi neipi, chimiro, kana fomu - zvakanyanya sezvo zvisingambokuvadze kushambadzira kwavo.
Nezve iyo kambani inovhenekera zvemukati kuburikidza neayo saiti, zvinyorwa, zvichena, nyaya dzenyaya kana bhurogu yayo yemubatanidzwa, ndinotenda kune matatu makiyi ekuti zvemukati zvako
... (446 chars skipped) ... 
yorwa kune mamwe masevhisi, kuburitswa kwenhau, isa zvinongedzo mumadirector, wedzera kune hurukuro mumaforamu akakodzera, kusimudzira zvinyorwa zvako kuburikidza nemagariro ekubhukimani maturusi, tumira kunzvimbo dzenhau, wikis, nezvimwe. Iva muenzi blogger uye utaure pane mamwe mablog ane ma link kumashure kune zvako zvemukati. Wedzera zvinongedzo kumavovovhoisi, ako masiginecha emaimeri, makadhi ako ebhizinesi… kwese kwese!

o chakakoshawo kurovera pasi zano. Semuenzaniso zano redu pachedu nderekuti:

Marokero inyika inonamata, uye sekureva kwa deginamajai nyika Chokwadi chebhuku, 99% yeMoroccans maMuslim. ChiKristu ndicho chechipiri chitendero chikuru uye chave chiri muMorocco kubvira pamberi pekuuya kweIslam. Kune maJuda mashoma munyika sezvo vazhinji vavo vadzokera kunyika dzakakomberedza, neIsrael ichitambira maJuda akadzoka. Mumakore achangopfuura huwandu hwevasina-chitendero hwave huri kuwedzera muMorocco.

Zvitendero uye vashoma vasingatendi kuna Mwari
Kuwanda kwemaJuda muMorocco kwakadzikiswa zvakanyanya zvichienzaniswa nenhamba dzakanyorwa munguva dzekare. Vazhinji kwazvo vakatamira kunharaunda yeIsrael iyo yakavambwa muna 1948. Vamwe vakatamira kuFrance neCanada.

Iyezvino mambo, King Mohammed VI, ane chinzvimbo chemutungamiri wezvematongerwo enyika uye "Muchinda weVatendi" (chikamu chezita rake repamutemo) - saka ane mamwe masimba ekutonga ematare emapazi ehurumende uye uye ari mutungamiriri wechitendero wenyika nevatungamiriri vezvitendero vese vari pasi ku.

Franchises 2020 yakanyanya yechinyakare, zvisinei, kuchine zvinopihwa zvinoenderana. Iwe unofanirwa kugara uchisarudza yakanakisa sarudzo kuti gare gare iwe usave nechero dambudziko. Kana iwe ukashanda pasi pefranchise, saka watove pakutanga iwe une mukana wakakosha, unonzwisisika, uye unokwanisa mumakwikwi emakwikwi. Inokupa iwe kugona kunyatso kutonga chero evaikwikwidza, zvinoreva kuti unonyatso kuhwina mumakwikwi. Kana iwe uchifarira franchise muna 2020, saka unononoka zvishoma. Mushure mezv

i, kana wakanganwa zvekushandisa zvekudzivirira, zvinogona kutengwa zviri nyore nemari.

Chido chose chekutenga chimwe chinhu kana kushandisa sevhisi chakanyangarika. Nhasi haisi 2020 muyadhi. MaFranchise akakura zvishoma uye akagadzira mwero wekuchengetedza. na imwe yakakodzera sarudzo nekuti vamiririri vefranchise vakaisa mari mukugadziriswa kwenzvimbo dzekurenda kusvika 2020.

Ndokusaka zvaive zvakakosha kuchengetedza kodzero yekuita zviitiko mukati meaya zvivakwa izvo vamiririri vemaki vagara kwenguva yakareba. Zvikwata zviviri zveMDC ndizvo zvakakwidza nyaya iyi. Asi ZANU-PF inoti haina chokuita netsamaba iyi, sezvo iri kuti dare rayo rePolitiburo ritange razeya nyaya iyi neChina.

wehurumende, pamwe nezviri kunetsa pakugovanwa kwemagavhuna ematunhu.

ZANU-PF inoti haina kubvuma zvekuti MDC inotungamirwa naVaTsvangirai itore magavhuna mashanu, ZANU-PF mana uye MDC yaVaMutambara mumwe.
ZANU-PF inoti izvi zvikaitwa inoda kupihwa chimwe chigaro chegurukota rinoshanda riri muhofisi yemutungamiri wenyika, kana kuti yotora mashanu, MDC inotungamirwa naVaMutambara yoshaya.
MDC iri kutarisirwawo kutaura nezvenyaya dziri kunetsa pamusangano wepagore uri kuitwa neChishanu muHarare. VaNelson Chamisa ndivo mutauriri weMDC.
VaChamisa vaudza Blessing Zulu weStudio7 kuti nyaya yekuti vakwira dare voga inoratidza kuti hapana kuwirirana kuri kuitika muhurumende yemubatanidzwa.

Zvisinei, baba vakakurumbira havana kurarama kusvika panguva iyo mwanakomana wavo akazozivikanwa pasi rese, asi ikozvino kusvikira Lindemann anogona kudada nedzinza rake rekusika.
Biography
Werner Lindemann akaberekwa muna 1926 mutaundi diki padyo neMagdeburg, mumhuri yakapusa. Vakarera mukomana zvine hukasha, mangwanani vakamudzidzisa pabasa remaoko. Asati apedza chikor
... (852 chars skipped) ... 
a ino Lindemann akagara muguta reDrispet.
Uye akatanga kunyora nhetembo pakarepo mushure mehondo. Uye chii chinoshamisa - idzi nhetembo dzake dzekutanga dzakaburitswa muunganidzwa "Zviteshi", uye ivo vainyanya kuve ehupenyu hwevanhu
Notoriety
Pakazosvika 1970, Lindemann akazove munyori akakurumbira uye mudetembi, uye vatsoropodzi vakatanga kumupemberera muzvinyorwa zvavo. Ivo vakanyora kuti anga aine yakajeka, yakajeka uye yakapusa nhetembo uye prose yevana. Akashandura zviitiko zvezuva nezuva k
... (852 chars skipped) ...
ba.
Chokwadi, aisatenda mukugona kwemwanakomana wake uye akatenda kuti haasi kuita izvo zvaaifanirwa kunge achiita. Kunyangwe Till Lindemann akatora tarenda rekunyora kwababa vake uye akanyora anopfuura gumi nemaviri mabhuku akanyorwa 18+.
Thiel akaberekwa muna 1963, uye mwanasikana akazvarwa kumhuri yaLindemann muna 1968.
Mudzimai waWerner Brigitte aive muimbi uye ainyora mabhuku. Vaviri vacho vakarambana apo Till achiri achiri kuyaruka.

Mumashoko kudare reCongress kuti riwedzere zvirango izvi, VaBiden vati: “Gore rose rapera vanoona nezvekudzivirirwa kwenyika yeZimbabwe, mapurisa, nevasori vange vachimbunyikidza vanhu uye kuita mhirizhonga yakananga nemapato anopikisa, vamiriri vevashandi uye vatori venhau.”
Vaenderera mberi vachiti, “Kushaikwa kweshanduko inoremekedza mutemo, hutongo hwejekerere, uye kodzero dzevanhu kuri kusiya vana veZimbabwe vari panguva yakaoma uye zvave kukonzera kusagadzikana kwedunhu rekuchamembe kweAfrica.”
Asi hurumende yeZimbabwe inoti yakatemerwa zvirango nekuda kwekuti yakatora minda kubva kuvachena ichipa vatema.
Kubva muna 2020 vakawedzera pamazita evakatemerwa zvirango vanosanganisira VaAnsele Sanyatwe vaive mukuru wemauto uye vave mumiriri weZimbabwe kuTanzania, vaive gurukota rezvevasori VaOwen Ncube uye VaKudakwashe Tagwirai muzvinabhizimisi vari chipangamazano chaVaMnangagwa.

Muzinda we Zimbabwe mu South Africa, wakaparura chirongwa chekubatsira zvizvarwa zveZimbabwe zviri munyika iyi kutora magwaro ekuzvarwa neekufambisa kana kuti "birth certificates and mapassports" senzira yekuderedza huwandu hwevanhu vari kutsvaga rubatsiro urwu.
Chirongwa ichi chichaitwa kwemasvondo maviri uye muzinda uyu uchange wakvhura mahofisi zuva rega rega Muvhuro kusvika Svondo. Mumwe mukuru kumuzinda uyu Amai Melody Chaurura vakaburitsa gwaro raitaura mafambiro echirongwa ichi nemusui weMuvhuro.
Chirongwa ichi chinonzi chiri kutarisira kubatsira vanhu chuiuru pazuva rega rega kwemazvondo maviri aya. Amai Chaurura vakati vanoda magwaro ekufambisa echimbi chimbi – Emergency Travel Documents vanogona kungouya kumahofisi avo panguiva dzebasa mazuva ose.
Mumwe mutauriri wesangano rinomirira zvizvarwa zveZimbabwe munyika yeSouth Africa, Muzvare Diana Zimbudzana vesangano reZimbabwe Exiles Forum vaudza Studio 7 kuti vana veZimbabwe vanotambirana nechirongwa ichi sezvo chiri kuvarerutsira kuwana magwaro akakosha aya. Panyaya yekuti vangabatsire vanodarika chiuru chimwe chete pazuva ava, Amai Zimbudzana vati vanotenda maruca vadya chakata.

Nhumwa dzemutungamiri weSouth Africa, VaJacob Zuma, dzapeta misangano yadzo nemapato matatu ari muhurumende yemubatanidzwa dzikakwanisa kupiwa magwaro epamire mapato matatu aya panyaya yehwaro hwesarudzo kana kuti elections road map.
Vane ruzivo nezviri kuitika vanoti nhumwa dzaVaZuma dzichitungamirwa naMuzvare Lindiwe Zulu dzinoti hadzisi kuda kuti munyika muitwe sarudzo pasati pavandudzwa mitemo inonzi nevakawanda iri kushandiswa neZanu-PF kubiridzira sarudzo.
Nhumwa idzi dziri kubuda pachena kuti zviri kudiwa neZanu-PF zvekuti paitwe sarudzo nechimbichimbi pasina kuvandudzwa hazvisi kuzotevedzerwa.
VaZuma vanonzi vari kuda kuti misariridzwa yeGlobal Political Agreement izadziswe ponyorwawo bumbiro idzva remitemo yenyika.
MDC inotungamirwa naVaMorgan Tsvangirai yakaendesawo gwaro riri kukurudzira masoja nemapurisa kuti asapindree munyaya dzesarudzo uye kuti pasave mhirizhonga panoitwa sarudzo.
VaZuma vave kutarisirwa kunogara pasi vonyora gwaro rine gwara richashandiswa pakuitwa sarudzo.
Nyanzvi munyaya dzezvematongerwo enyika, VaTrevor Maisiri, vanoti panyaya yekuvandudza zvinhu muZimbabwe kutenda maruva wadya chakata.

GORE RINO ndinoda kuti uite se gondo.
Inzwa zvidzidzo 4 kubva kugondo
1: Gondo ndomambo weshiri dzose. Rinobhururuka kusvika kumakore kusingasvike dzimwe shiri.
Mwari ngavakusimudze kusvika pamusoro soro pasati pasvikwa chero nani kudzinza kwenyu.
2: Gondo haritye dutu.
Ndoda kuti usatye zvauchasangana nazvo, nhamo nematambudziko.. Kungava kufirwa, kurwarirwa kana kushaiwa.
Ndati gore rino usatya ita se gondo, rinoenda kurikubva dutu.
Panohwanda dzimwe shiri iro rinovhima.
3: Gondo rinoona chero kanhu kadiki riri muchadenga.
Iva nemaziso anoona mikana yakanaka. Tsvaga chekuita kana chekutengesa. Ona pane mikana segondo. Iva nemaziso anoona pane mari. Usangochema chema, tengesa chero musika chaiwo.
4: Gondo rinobata chero nyoka.
Vavengi vako ngavazive kuti hautangike. Wana nguva yekutsanya uchiverengawo bhaibheri rako.
Zvese zviri kugadzirwa nemuvengi ngazviparare nezita raJesu Kristu.

Musangano we World Diamond Council wepagore wakatanga neMuvhuro mu St Petersburg ku Russia, uko nyaya yemangoda ekwaMarange iri kukurukurwa nezvayo nemusi weChina.
Kimberly Process iri kutarisirwa kuvhota kuti Zimbabwe yopihwa mvumo here kana kuti kwete yekutengesa mangoda ekwaMarange.
Vazhinji vari kupinda mumusangano uyu vanonzi vari kuwirirana kuti dai Zimbabwe yabvumidzwa kutengesa mangoda ayo. Mumiriri weZimbabwe mu Russia, Va Happyson Muchechetere, vanonzi vakataura pamusangano uyu neMuvhuro vachikurudzira nhengo dze KP neWorld Diamond Council kuti dzipe Zimbabwe mvumo yekutengesa mangoda ayo.
Mutungamiri we International Diamond Manufacturers, Va Moti Ganz, vanonzi vaudza musangano uyu kuti mangoda ekwa Marange akachena, nokudaro anofanira kutengeswa pamisika yepasi rose.
Kimberly Process yakatadza kupa Zimbabwe mvumo yekutengesa mangoda ekwaMarange, kunyange hazvo nhumwa yesangano iri kuZimbabwe, VaAbbey Chikane, vakanyora gwaro rinokurudzira kuti mangoda ekwaMarange atengeswe.
Va Dewa Mavhinga vanoshanda neCrisis in Zimbabwe Coalition, uye vari kutevera zviri kuitika pamangoda ekwaMarange. Va Mavhinga vanoti pane zvizhinji zvinoda kuitwa Zimbabwe isati yaphiwa mvumo yekutengesa mangoda ayo.

Gadzira Yako HPMC Capsule
Gadzira Yako Yega Capsules
Masevhisi edu ekugadzira anopa tsika HPMC isina chinhu capsules mune akasiyana mavara, marudzi uye mhando.Sevanopa HPMC capsule vagadziri uye vagadziri vecapsule, isu tine hunyanzvi mukupa vegan capsule shells kuzadzisa zvaunoda chaizvo.Vimba nesu kuti tipe mhando yepamusoro uye customizable HPMC capsules kune bhizinesi rako kana zvaunoda iwe pachako.
Types
Yasin ndivo vanotungamira mugadziri we customizable HPMC isina chinhu muriwo capsules.Masevhisi edu ekugadzira anopa akasiyana emhando dzekapisi, kusanganisira opaque, translucent uye pearl yekupedzisa sarudzo, kuzadzisa zvaunoda chaizvo.
Color
Yedu yekugadzira sevhisi inopa tsika vegan isina chinhu capsule mavara kuti aenderane zvaunoda.Bata isu kuti uwane emhando yepamusoro, yakavimbika capsules yechigadzirwa chako.
Dhinda Logo Yako
Kune yakasarudzika HPMC capsules, yedu yekugadzira sevhisi inobvumira kudhindwa kwetsika logos.Isu tiri vatengesi vakavimbika vemhando yepamusoro HPMC Capsules.Kana uine zvido zvekudhinda, tapota taura nesu.
Kuti ugadzire yako capsules, ndapota ipa iyo inotevera ruzivo
1) Ukuru hunodiwa hwema capsules.
2) Nhamba yePantone yekugadzirisa mavara.
3) Tsanangudzo yepamusoro logo mifananidzo kana zvinyorwa zveAI kuti zvishandiswe kudhinda.
4) Zvingave zvinobatsira kupa zvinyorwa zveAI izvo zvinosanganisira zvese zvakagadziridzwa senge ruvara, logo nzvimbo, uye saizi.

Chirongwa cheHarare International Festival Of The Arts (HIFA) chegore rino chatanga nemutsindo muHarare gardens nhasi apo nyanzvi dzekuimba nemitambo dzinobva pasi rose dzichange dzichiratidza hunyanzvi hadzo kwemazuva matanhatu anotevera.
Nyanzvi dzemunyika dzinosvika chiuru dzichange dziri pamitambo iyi. Mitambo iyi iri pasi pedingindira rinonzi, “A show of spirit” iri kutarisirwa kunakidza veruzhinji avo vachawana mukana wekupembere ra bhavhadheyi remuimbi ane mukurumbira, oliver mtukudzi, uyo achange achisvitsa makore makumi matanhatu muna gunyana gore rino.
Mtukudzi achaimba nemumwe muimbi wekusenegal ane mukurumbira, Ismael Lo kuTelecel main stage muHarare gardens neSvondo.
Mutambo weHIFA wave nemakore gumi nematu ichiitwa muHarare. Vanowona nezvekufambiswa kwemashoko mu HIFA, vaTafadzwa Simba, vaudza Marvellous Mhlanga Nyahuye weStudio7 kuti vari kufanzwa nemafambiro ari hurongwa hwavo.

Dhipatimendi reUnited States rakasimudza yambiro yaro yekuVenezuela yezvekufamba kune vagari vemuUS kuti "vasafambe," zvichiratidza kusagadzikana kwevanhu.
Dhipatimendi rakaburitsa yambiro yeteyiti 4 pamusi weChipiri masikati, ichinyevera vanhu vekuAmerica kuti vadzivise nyika nekuda kwe "mhosva, kusagadzikana kwevanhu, hupfumi husina kunaka," uye "kusunga nekusungwa zvisina tsarukano" kwevagari vemuUS.
Iro zano nyowani rekufamba rinoyambira vagari vemuUS nezve "kusagadzikana kwezvematongerwo enyika" uye mukana wekuti vabatwe nemaratidziro ane chisimba emumigwagwa ayo anogona kuitika "pasina chiziviso."
Yambiro "zvine simba" inokurudzira kuti vagari vemuUS vakazvimirira vasiye Venezuela, vachiisa Venezuela muchikamu chimwe chete seSyria neNorth Korea. Izvo zvinouya mazuva mushure mekunge US yaraira kubviswa kwevashandi vasiri vechimbichimbi kubva kumumiriri wayo muCaracas, izvo zvasiya ne "kugona kushoma" kwekupa rubatsiro rwechimbichimbi kuvagari vekuUS ikoko.
United States yakawedzera kumanikidza kuVenezuela svondo rapfuura, ichiziva mutungamiri anopikisa semutungamiriri wenyika uye achikumbira Maduro kuti abve pachigaro. Washington yakatemera zvirango kukambani yemafuta yeVenezuela PDVSA nemusi weMuvhuro, zvichipa mhosva kubva kugurukota rezvekunze kwenyika kuti US yaida kuita coup.

SINOTRUK HOVA terminal tirakita rori
Terminal lorry Tractor Truck
Iine dhizaini yakavimbika uye yakagadzikana yedhizaini, yakakura kubereka simba, yakanakisa injini simba, kuita kwakadzikama zvakanyanya, uye furemu yayo yakaumbwa mumaindasitiri ekuvaka uye emigodhi ine nharaunda yakashata yekushanda, inoshandiswa zvakanyanya pakutakura midziyo.Inogamuchirwa zvakanyanya nevashandisi.Pasina chero mubvunzo, rori yedu yetarakita NO.1 sarudzo yeprojekti yako.
Zvigadzirwa zvedu zvikuru zvinobva kuDump Truck, Tractor Truck, Concrete Mixer Truck, Van Truck, Lorry Truck, Off-road Dump Truck, Tanker Truck, Truck Mounted Cranes, trailer, tanker trailer uye mamwe marudzi ese akagadziridzwa marori.Tinogona kugadzira, kugadzira uye kupa vatengi vedu chero yakakosha mota.
Nyanzvi muindasitiri yemarori kweanopfuura makore gumi, tinoziva kuti marori ndeapi, uye izvo vatengi vanonyatsoda.Isu tinogona kukurudzira kutsanangurwa kwevatengi.
Marori edu nematrailer anotumirwa kunze kwenyika dzinopfuura makumi matanhatu nenzvimbo, dzakadai sePhilippines, Russia, Africa, South East Asia, North Asia, Middle East, South America zvichingodaro.
One-stop sevhisi kune ese marori nematiraire kubva kuChina, isu tine imwe sevhisi chiteshi kunze kwenyika, uye inopa kekutanga sevhisi kune mutengi.
Tine zvigadzirwa zvakasiyana-siyana, zvinogona kusangana nezvinodiwa neprojekti yevatengi.

Chiratidzo:
Kana uchivhura gwaro reIzwi rakakanganiswa neMicrosoft Word, dialog ye "File Conversion" inomuka ndokukumbira kuti usarudze encoding inoita kuti gwaro rako riverenge.
Nekudaro, chero coding ipi yaunosarudza, zvirimo zvekutanga zvegwaro hazvife zvakadzorerwa.
Tsananguro chaiyo:
Kana iyo encoding yeruzivo iri muIzwi gwaro yakaora kana lost, Shoko harizokwanisi kutsanangura zvirimo mugwaro. Saka ichakwenya dialog yekushandura faira uye ndokumbira iyo chaiyo encoding. Uye nekuda kwehuwori hwechimiro chefaira nezvimwe zvirimo, kunyangwe ukasarudza kukodha kwakakodzera, Shoko richiri kutadza kududzira zvirimo nemazvo, izvo zvinopa gwaro risingaverengeke uye risingabatsiri. Mumamiriro ezvinhu akadaro, unogona kushandisa chigadzirwa chedu DataNumen Word Repair kugadzirisa iro gwaro reIzwi uye kugadzirisa iyi kukanganisa.
Semuenzaniso Faira:
Semuenzaniso huwori hweGwaro refaira faira rinokonzeresa iko kukanganisa. Kukanganisa7_1.doc
Iyo faira yakagadziriswa ne DataNumen Word Repair: Kukanganisa7_1_fixed.doc

Musangano mukuru wevanhukadzi wanga uchiitirwa muZimbabwe wapera neChina muHarare uchikurudzira mutungamiriri wenyika, Va Robert Mugabe, mutungamiri wehurumende, Va Morgan Tsvangirai, pamwe nemutevedzeri waVaTsvangirai, Va Arthur Mutambara, kuti vaite zvese zvavanogona kuita kuitira kuti zvinhu zvifambe zvakanaka munyika.
Mutevedzeri wemutungamiri weWomen’s Coalition, Muzvare Rutendo Hadebe, vanoti madzimai awirirana kuti hapana chinokwanisa kushandurwa mumatambudziko avanosangana nawo kana nhepfenyuro dzakazvimirira dzisina kuvhurwa munyika, uye kana mapepanhau akazvimirira asati atanga kuita basa rawo.
Vaimbova mutungamiri weIreland, Amai Mary Robinson, ndivo vange vari munyarikani pamusangano wemazuva matatu uyu.
Muzvare Hadebe vanoti zvakakosha kuti dzinhepfenyuro itsva dzitange kushanda munyika, kuitira kuti vanhukadzi vakwanise kusvitsa kuvanhu vakawanda zvirongwa zvavo zvakanangana nebudiriro.
Musangano uyu wakavhurwa naVaMugabe neChipiri, uye vamwe vakuru vakuru muhurumende, vakapinda mumusangano uyu vachinzwa matambudziko ari kusangana nevanhukadzi.
